## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not capture all recent developments in climate change research. The complexity of climate change impacts means that some nuances may be overlooked. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of climate science and policy can lead to changes in understanding and priorities. Further research and continuous monitoring are essential to keep abreast of new findings and implications.